# Large Data Files (Ignore uncompressed files to prevent GitHub push failures)
# The 192MB uncompressed dataset must be ignored:
data/processed/final_dataset_with_recommendations.csv
# The 43MB compressed version (final_dataset_with_recommendations.csv.gz) is tracked and pushed!

# Ignore intermediate/large raw data files if they are not required by the web app:
data/merged_city_crime_data.csv
data/raw/
data/interim/
raw_data/

# Model files (keep them as they are small and needed for predictions)
!outputs/models/*.pkl
